  <body>
    <span charset="utf-8" style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; font-weight: normal; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); float: none; letter-spacing: normal; font-size: medium; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Bitstream Vera Serif, Times New Roman, serif; text-align: start; word-spacing: 0px"><font face="Bitstream Vera Serif, Times New Roman, serif" size="medium" color="rgb(34, 34, 34)">2014 Grammy-nominated producer/songwriter seeks an expert drawbar-puller for an original rock &amp; soul project. Think QOTSA meets Tina Turner. Stax meets Sabbath. Modern heavy rock meets vintage 60s soul.</font></span><font face="Bitstream Vera Serif, Times New Roman, serif" size="medium" color="rgb(34, 34, 34)"><br style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal; word-spacing: 0px" align="start"/><br style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal; word-spacing: 0px" align="start"/><span style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font-weight: normal; float: none; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium; letter-spacing: normal; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Bitstream Vera Serif, Times New Roman, serif; text-align: start; word-spacing: 0px">Whether you play a B-3 through a 122, or just have a damn good emulator, you should know the tricks of of the trade. Wild Bill Davis, Jimmy Smith and Larry Young should be familiar names to you. At the same time, you should be able to rock out when needed (and it will be needed). You'll be soloing, so solid improv should be in your skill set.</span><br style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal; word-spacing: 0px" align="start"/><br style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal; word-spacing: 0px" align="start"/><span style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font-weight: normal; float: none; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium; letter-spacing: normal; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Bitstream Vera Serif, Times New Roman, serif; text-align: start; word-spacing: 0px">If interested, please include link to audio/video in your email and let us know a little bit about yourself. Thanks!</span><br style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal; word-spacing: 0px" align="start"/><br style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; font-variant: normal; line-height: normal; word-spacing: 0px" align="start"/><span style="white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font-weight: normal; float: none; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-size: medium; letter-spacing: normal; font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Bitstream Vera Serif, Times New Roman, serif; text-align: start; word-spacing: 0px">Keywords: Keyboardist, keyboards, organ, organist, Hammond, Wurlitzer, Rhodes, piano, pianist, Jimmy Smith, Booker T, John Lord, Keith Emerson, Joey DeFrancesco, Rick Wakeman, Greg Allman, Ken Hensley</span></font>
